    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">玩</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">戲</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>ACT NOT SERIOUSLY so as to CAUSE ONESELF to BECOME DELIGHTED.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Wán 玩 "play" refers to the act of amusing oneself.</p>
<p>2. Xì 戲 refers to playful pleasantry, the playing of linguistic games.</p>
<p>3. Yóu xí 遊戲 refers to playful fun-seeking which involves physical movement.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>遊戲</p>
